scripts.build: yarn clean && yarn build:esm && yarn build:cjs && yarn build:scripts
scripts.build:esm: NODE_OPTIONS=--max-old-space-size=4096 tsc --outDir dist/ && rm -rf dist/tests dist/**/tests
scripts.build:cjs: NODE_OPTIONS=--max-old-space-size=4096 tsc --outDir dist-cjs/ -p tsconfig.cjs.json && node scripts/move-cjs-to-dist.js && rm -rf dist-cjs
scripts.lint: NODE_OPTIONS=--max-old-space-size=4096 eslint src && dpdm --exit-code circular:1 --no-warning --no-tree src/*.ts src/**/*.ts
scripts.clean: rm -rf dist/ && NODE_OPTIONS=--max-old-space-size=4096 node scripts/create-entrypoints.js pre
